  truth --> review
  review -->|"reviewed ecosystem summaries"| x64source
  review -->|"reviewed manuals, references, reports, bundles"| dotsource

  x64site -->|"deep technical and artifact links"| dotsite
  dotsite -->|"engine, product, campus, and project-context links"| x64site
  dotsite -->|"reviewed artifact notices and route summaries"| review

  separate["Independent releases\nnot mirrors: separate source trees, route ownership, builds, and histories"]:::output
